pango 1.56.4 calls FcFreeTypeQueryAll() in pango_fc_font_map_add_font_file
but never includes <fontconfig/fcfreetype.h>, the only header that declares
it -- and pango compiles with -Werror=implicit. Distro builds mask this
through toolchain defaults; a clean cross build does not. Fixed upstream
after 1.56; drop this patch on the next pango bump if it no longer applies.

--- a/pango/pangofc-fontmap.c	2026-07-23 01:22:56.782520000 +0300
+++ b/pango/pangofc-fontmap.c	2026-07-23 01:22:56.850788800 +0300
@@ -47,6 +47,7 @@
 #include "pango-coverage-private.h"
 #include "pango-trace-private.h"
 #include <hb-ft.h>
+#include <fontconfig/fcfreetype.h>
 
 
